MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping load the data from SUPPLY,GROSS_PRIORITIZED_DEMAND and DPR_ITEM into TASER_NETTING.
MAPPING.NAME: m_TASER_NETTING

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression transformation to calculate the QUANTITIES & ALLOC quantities
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_NETTING

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_OH<>0 AND V_DMD >=0), IIF((V_OH >= V_DMD), (V_OH-V_DMD), 0), V_OH)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_OH_QTY

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_OH<>0 AND V_DMD >=0), IIF((V_OH >= V_DMD), V_DMD, V_OH), 0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_OH_ALLOC

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_OH<>0 AND V_DMD >=0), IIF((V_OH >= V_DMD), 0, V_DMD-V_OH), V_DMD)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_DMD1

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_IT<>0 AND V_DMD1 >=0), IIF((V_IT >= V_DMD1), (V_IT-V_DMD1), 0), V_IT)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_IT_QTY

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_IT<>0 AND V_DMD1 >=0), IIF((V_IT >= V_DMD1), V_DMD1, V_IT), 0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_IT_ALLOC

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_IT<>0 AND V_DMD1 >=0), IIF((V_IT >= V_DMD1), 0, V_DMD1-V_IT), V_DMD1)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_DMD2

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_PO<>0 AND V_DMD2 >=0), IIF((V_PO >= V_DMD2), (V_PO-V_DMD2), 0), V_PO)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_PO_QTY

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_PO<>0 AND V_DMD2 >=0), IIF((V_PO >= V_DMD2), V_DMD2, V_PO), 0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_PO_ALLOC

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_PO<>0 AND V_DMD2 >=0), IIF((V_PO >= V_DMD2), 0, V_DMD2-V_PO), V_DMD2)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_DMD3

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_FIRM_WIP<>0 AND V_DMD3 >=0), IIF((V_FIRM_WIP >= V_DMD3), (V_FIRM_WIP-V_DMD3), 0), V_FIRM_WIP)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_FIRM_WIP_QTY

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((V_FIRM_WIP<>0 AND V_DMD3 >=0), IIF((V_FIRM_WIP >= V_DMD3), V_DMD3, V_FIRM_WIP), 0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_FIRM_WIP_ALLOC

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Soource qualifier will extract the data from sources.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_SUPPLY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT gpd.AS_OF_DATE, gpd.ITEM_ID, NVL(di.ITEM_CODE,dj.ITEM_CODE) ITEM_CODE, gpd.plant, sum(case when NVL(SUPPLY.ONHAND_UNITS,0) + case when supply.reworks_units <0 then supply.reworks_units end <0 then 0 else NVL(SUPPLY.ONHAND_UNITS,0) + nvl(case when supply.reworks_units <0 then supply.reworks_units end,0) end) ONHAND_UNITS, sum(SUPPLY.INTRANSIT_UNITS) INTRANSIT_UNITS, sum(SUPPLY.PO_UNITS) PO_UNITS, sum(NVL(SUPPLY.FIRM_WIP_UNITS,0) + nvl(case when supply.reworks_units >0 then supply.reworks_units end,0)) FIRM_WIP_UNITS, gpd.RULE_NUMBER, gpd.DEMAND_SOURCE, gpd.PRIORITY_SEQUENCE, gpd.CURRENT_QTY, gpd.CRITICAL_RATIO, gpd.SPREAD_CRITICAL_RATIO, gpd.DEMAND_CLASS FROM GROSS_PRIORITIZED_DEMAND gpd --left outer join SUPPLY supply left outer join (Select item_id, demand_loc, sum(onhand_units) onhand_units, sum(reworks_units) reworks_units, sum(intransit_units) intransit_units, sum(po_units) po_units, sum(firm_wip_units) firm_wip_units from SUPPLY group by item_id, demand_loc) supply on supply.item_id = gpd.item_id and supply.demand_loc=gpd.plant ---and gpd.demand_source not like 'FCST%' and gpd.demand_driver <>'KERP' and di.status ='A' left join (select * from dpr_item where status = 'A' and NOT (manufacturing_product_family= 'DCTIL' and primary_dc = dc_code)) di on gpd.style =di.aps_style_cd and gpd.color =di.aps_color_cd and gpd.size_cd =di.size_code and gpd.attribute_cd=di.attribute_code and gpd.plant =di.dc_code left join (select * from dpr_item where status = 'A' and manufacturing_product_family <> 'DCTIL' ) dj on gpd.style =dj.aps_style_cd and gpd.color =dj.aps_color_cd and gpd.size_cd =dj.size_code and gpd.attribute_cd=dj.attribute_code where gpd.demand_source not like 'FCST%' and gpd.demand_driver <>'KERP' group by gpd.AS_OF_DATE, gpd.ITEM_ID, NVL(di.ITEM_CODE,dj.ITEM_CODE), gpd.plant, gpd.RULE_NUMBER, gpd.DEMAND_SOURCE, gpd.PRIORITY_SEQUENCE, gpd.CURRENT_QTY, gpd.CRITICAL_RATIO, gpd.SPREAD_CRITICAL_RATIO, gpd.DEMAND_CLASS order by NVL(di.ITEM_CODE,dj.ITEM_CODE),gpd.RULE_NUMBER,gpd.PRIORITY_SEQUENCE
